"IAS40_P0306">on disposal of investment property not carried at             fair value:</p>           <ol base="SL46592023" id="IAS40_L0035" type="lower-roman"><li id="IAS40_78_d_i">               <li_value>(i)</li_value>               <p base="SL46592025" id="IAS40_P0307">the fact that the entity has disposed of                 investment property not carried at fair value;</p>             </li><li id="IAS40_78_d_ii">               <li_value>(ii)</li_value>               <p base="SL46592028" id="IAS40_P0308">the <xref base="SL46590576" href="IAS40_5.dita#IAS40_5/IAS40_P0044">carrying amount<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0027"/></ph></xref> of that investment property at                 the time of sale; and</p>             </li><li id="IAS40_78_d_iii">               <li_value>(iii)</li_value>               <p base="SL46592032" id="IAS40_P0309">the amount of gain or loss recognised.</p>             </li></ol>         </li></ol>     </variant></body></paragraph>